[http://kasda.cn/product_info.asp?k=&id=199 Product page]
The device is labeled as a '''Cyberoam''' NetGenie in the FCC external photos.
Additional (electrically identical) models of KW5212, NG11VO, and NG11VH are specified in the test report.
*LAN: 4x ports (1x GbE + 3x FE)
Default settings (including the SSID) and the used OUI (00:0E:F4 ['''Kasda''']) are per the FCC manual. They may be inaccurate.
The power adapter shown in the FCC external photos is an ''unbranded'' ADS012PM-W 120100 (100-240VAC ~ 50-60Hz, 0.5A -> 12VDC, 1.0A).
US: U5IDL01BKW5212
